Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren’t such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don’t hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, you’re the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they want to change something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plea from a Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this intimidating power?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was that\Nred Chakra earlier on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this guy a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’m telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not gonna let the likes\Nof Orochimaru get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m telling you that I’ll stop you…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means breaking\Nevery bone in your arm and legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style:\NFire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Wake up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t come to your senses,\NI'll have to break your bones
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you can’t move\Nand I'll take you home that way, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck do you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who has neither parents nor brothers,\Nthink you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think that you,\Nwho's been all alone from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can understand anything about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because I have the ties\Nthat I feel this agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you possibly understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what it feels like to lose all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true that I can’t understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how it feels to really\Nhave parents or brothers…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my treat today…\NEat your fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I’m with Iruka Sensei,\NI imagine…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Dig in! 					– Dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja, first of all, need to\Nwarm their inner man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Don’t get too carried away\Nand overeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is…\Nwhat it feels like to have a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I’m with you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, idiot, idiot…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, you loser?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not gonna lose to you,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and say\Nwhatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not start feeling\Ntoo comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder…if having a brother\Nfeels something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it, Naruto…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that you go to\Nthis extent for me…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me it’s a tie that\NI’ve finally been able to have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:07:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’m gonna stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too late, Naruto…\Nlt’s already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t go back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\NI just have to cut that tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why wear that headband now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll acknowledge you…\NYou’re strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason for that is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’re someone who knows\Nthe pain of solitude as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that pain makes people stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that very reason,\Nby cutting that tie,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be able to obtain\Neven greater strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight you now on equal terms.\NHowever…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even be able to\Ninflict a scratch on my forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s something that\Nwon’t change in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that whatever I say\Nwon’t have any effect anymore, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m done with talking…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, it’s only fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m able to see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m now able to see\Nthis guy’s movements…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which I wasn’t able to see before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m able to see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke’s moving completely\Ndifferent from a few moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn’t care less!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I can’t afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the influence of my body\Ngetting used to the state of Curse Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he moves…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the subtle movements in\Nthe way he exerts his strength…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can vividly see\Nan image of his next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my level of “eyes,”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need to use unnecessary Chakra\Nand can instead preserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Curse Mark takes\Ntoo much Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can see this much…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can time my attacks to the images of\NNaruto’s movements as I foresee them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s totally reading my movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no mistake it’s this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better hurry.\NI have a bad premonition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style:\NDragon Flame Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-su-ke…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too late, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too late now! Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak, aren’t you, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be grateful to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to the Fourth Hokage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who contained me within\Nthe likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I’m able to read\NNaruto’s movements completely…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his Chakra makes\Na separate move of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the Chakra itself is moving\Nin accordance with its own will…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with my “eyes”\NI’m unable to read it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That red Chakra…\Nthat’s not an ordinary Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your target is Naruto, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To abduct Naruto\Nis the No.1 priority
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,placed by our organization, Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you have\Nsome kind of special power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style:\NFire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Chakra is protecting him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t be caught as long as\NI fight from distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it… This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is dodge…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me get there in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, gimme a break…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get tainted by this power …
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t even know what\Nwill happen to me in the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it can’t be helped,\Ncan it, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is certainly true\Nthat you were special…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am even more special than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as though\NI had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:22:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Held in my two hands\NA droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Softly clutching forgotten memories\NLost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll keep these thoughts…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! My body hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to make it worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve completely lost feeling\Nin my left arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently this power\Nisn’t something that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can just keep on using continuously!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But …I can’t give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.68,0:23:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My next blow is\Ngoing to be the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: “The End of Tears”
